<br>
Also I am not quite sure how many HPs rogue gets per stamina point, for me it seems 3 HPs at level 60. So losing 9 hit points is not a big deal. Str increases your attack, and thats what rogues are all about. And you would need those Dex points at level 60 when you start assassinating stuff, so belt is a good upgrade.  Losing AC for a rogue is not a big deal. I have below 1100 AC, and I am not complaining. Skilled rogue is not supposed to get hit.<br>
<br>
Hands is a very nice upgrade.<br>
<br>
2nd melee, I'd get a faster weapon. Something like crystal spider fang, or Trakasaur's tooth.<br>
<br>
